Paul T. GOODWIN, petitioner,
v.
Troy STEELE, Warden. No. 14-7464 14A618. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 10, 2014.

Opinion *781Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him referred to the Court is denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
